1
00:00:16,057 --> 00:00:19,611
택시 창밖으로 번지는 불빛
Lights blurring outside the taxi window.

2
00:00:20,945 --> 00:00:25,643
라디오에서 흘러나온 옛날 노래
An old song playing on the radio.

3
00:00:26,719 --> 00:00:31,739
이 시간엔 모든 게 느려져
Everything slows down at this hour.

4
00:00:31,867 --> 00:00:35,926
너한테 갈까 말까 고민만 해
I just keep wondering whether to go to you or not.

5
00:00:37,893 --> 00:00:43,149
편의점 앞 벤치에 앉아서
Sitting on a bench in front of the convenience store,

6
00:00:43,621 --> 00:00:46,570
따뜻한 캔 하나 손에 쥐고
Holding a warm can in my hand.

7
00:00:46,570 --> 00:00:52,859
네 연락을 기다리는 건 아닌데
It's not like I'm waiting for your call,

8
00:00:53,229 --> 00:00:57,142
자꾸 화면을 확인하게 돼
But I keep checking my screen.

9
00:00:57,801 --> 00:01:02,670
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
A 2 AM night when the frequency matches,

10
00:01:02,670 --> 00:01:07,590
잡음 사이로 네 목소리가 들려
I can hear your voice through the static.

11
00:01:07,590 --> 00:01:13,281
이 도시가 잠들면 우리만 깨어서
When this city falls asleep, only we stay awake,

12
00:01:13,582 --> 00:01:18,269
같은 하늘 아래 다른 곳에서
In different places under the same sky.

13
00:01:18,269 --> 00:01:22,709
옥상에서 내려다본 골목길
The alleyway seen from the rooftop,

14
00:01:22,709 --> 00:01:25,195
가로등 하나가 깜빡이고 있어
A streetlamp is flickering.

15
00:01:25,310 --> 00:01:28,030
하고 싶은 말은 루프처럼 돌아
The words I want to say go around in a loop,

16
00:01:28,030 --> 00:01:30,605
입 밖으론 한마디도 못 꺼내
But I can't utter a single word.

17
00:01:30,784 --> 00:01:33,709
이어폰 한쪽만 끼고 걸어
I walk with only one earphone in,

18
00:01:33,709 --> 00:01:36,231
네가 좋아하던 그 노래 틀어
Playing that song you used to like.

19
00:01:36,545 --> 00:01:38,609
발걸음이 리듬을 타는 밤
A night where my footsteps follow the rhythm,

20
00:01:38,609 --> 00:01:41,234
혼자인데 혼자가 아닌 것 같아
I'm alone, but it doesn't feel like I am.

21
00:01:41,424 --> 00:01:45,349
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
A 2 AM night when the frequency matches,

22
00:01:45,349 --> 00:01:50,250
잡음 사이로 네 목소리가 들려
I can hear your voice through the static.

23
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:55,870
이 도시가 잠들면 우리만 깨어서
When this city falls asleep, only we stay awake,

24
00:01:56,334 --> 00:02:01,085
같은 하늘 아래 다른 곳에서
In different places under the same sky.

25
00:02:03,969 --> 00:02:06,329
전화할까 말까 세 번째 고민
Wondering for the third time if I should call,

26
00:02:06,329 --> 00:02:11,796
나도 지금 네 번호 보고 있어
I'm also looking at your number right now.

27
00:02:12,777 --> 00:02:17,270
새벽 두 시 주파수가 맞는 밤
A 2 AM night when the frequency matches,

28
00:02:17,270 --> 00:02:22,030
잡음 속에서 결국 너를 찾아
In the static, I finally find you.

29
00:02:22,030 --> 00:02:27,770
이 도시가 잠들어도 우리는 깨어서
Even if this city sleeps, we stay awake,

30
00:02:27,921 --> 00:02:57,129
같은 주파수로 이어져 있어
We're connected by the same frequency.

